narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Good class, you probably have to take it anyway. Similar difficulty to intro to naval science, similar workload. You will learn the basics of Navigation and have some fun doing it while disliking all of the assignments and exams.
Yes, its a good course and you'll learn a lot about marine navigation.
Navigation. All students who are taking this course will be required to take it, so I highly recommend it.
I would recommend that other students than NROTC midshipmen should take the class.
A hands-on class teaching one to navigate. I would highly recommend this class to anyone interested in the subject.
